data.description: Lovingly maintained 4BR/ 3 BA 4-sided brick ranch with full walkout basement! Featuring hardwood floors throughout the first floor- with vinyl flooring in the kitchen and den. The kitchen features high-end stainless steel appliances, a gas Viking cooktop, and a KitchenAid electric wall oven. The eat-in kitchen also has more than ample storage, solid surface countertops along with solid wood cabinetry. Plus a large laundry/mudroom area adds extra space and storage. All bedrooms are sizeable with reasonable closet space, The Master suite has a walk-in shower. With multiple living spaces, this home has more than enough room for everyone. The Den features a wonderful wood-burning fireplace perfect for those chilly evenings, the patio doors open off the den and overlook a beautiful fenced yard the ideal space for all the family.   The basement makes an ideal space for guests with its own bedroom and bathroom. This home is move-in ready in popular Green Acres blocks to the UGA Vet School, Kroger, and many restaurants!
